<font size="5"><b>California Pizza Kitchen is opening a new restaurant in <a href="https://higherme.com/locations/586513be35dec?utm_source=craigslist&amp;utm_medium=job_board&amp;utm_campaign=l%3A1560%3Amililani%7Cc%3A104%3Acalifornia_pizza_kitchen&amp;utm_content=day-wednesday" rel="nofollow">Mililani, HI</a> and is now hiring for all positions online!</font></b>

<center><a href="https://higherme.com/locations/586513be35dec?utm_source=craigslist&amp;utm_medium=job_board&amp;utm_campaign=l%3A1560%3Amililani%7Cc%3A104%3Acalifornia_pizza_kitchen&amp;utm_content=day-wednesday" rel="nofollow">
<img border="0" alt="HigherMe_Apply" src="http://www.jrctransportation.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/applynow-button.png" width="232" height="100"></a></center>

<br> 
 <br> <h2></h2> <h3>Who Are We?</h3> <font size="4">


This is the place for TASTE makers, RULE breakers and EARTH shakers who conquer challenges by daring to work on the edge and thinking outside the box. We call ourselves the EPIC Nation because we are all working toward a common goal around the world, and we have the most amazing time doing it. We bring the BIGGEST and BEST parts of ourselves to work and to our communities, and that simple idea just makes us better as a whole. Our philosophy is when you have a passion for something, there's no stopping you. So at CPK, go ahead. Be Bold. Be You. Be EPIC. We are the EPIC Nation.
<br><br>
Who doesn't like contests on the regular where the prizes are Ipads, free food, gift cards, X-Boxes, etc.? Also, where else does your team and your regulars consider you to be as close as family? We know, we're pretty awesome. Check us out and apply today!
</font> <br> <br>


 <h3>Who Are We Looking For?</h3> <font size="4">
<b>Now hiring for our new restaurant opening in Mililani! Apply in person (or apply online) beginning 1/4/17 Mon-Sat 9AM to 6PM at the Mililani Shopping center, 95-390 Kuahelani Ave., Mililani, HI 96789 between Foodland &amp; The Shack. </b>

<br><br>

We are looking for bright and energetic people to join our brand new team. Now hiring for all positions, including:
<br><strong>
<ul><li><a href="https://higherme.com/jobs/5865146c7b88d?utm_source=craigslist&amp;utm_medium=job_board&amp;utm_campaign=j%3A4274%3Arestaurant_bartender%7Cl%3A1560%3Amililani%7Cc%3A104%3Acalifornia_pizza_kitchen&amp;utm_content=day-wednesday" rel="nofollow">Restaurant Bartender</a></li>

<li><a href="https://higherme.com/jobs/5865146d9f2e4?utm_source=craigslist&amp;utm_medium=job_board&amp;utm_campaign=j%3A4275%3Arestaurant_bussers%7Cl%3A1560%3Amililani%7Cc%3A104%3Acalifornia_pizza_kitchen&amp;utm_content=day-wednesday" rel="nofollow">Restaurant Bussers</a></li>

<li><a href="https://higherme.com/jobs/5865146eb71d9?utm_source=craigslist&amp;utm_medium=job_board&amp;utm_campaign=j%3A4276%3Arestaurant_cook%7Cl%3A1560%3Amililani%7Cc%3A104%3Acalifornia_pizza_kitchen&amp;utm_content=day-wednesday" rel="nofollow">Restaurant Cook</a></li>

<li><a href="https://higherme.com/jobs/58651470a3b90?utm_source=craigslist&amp;utm_medium=job_board&amp;utm_campaign=j%3A4277%3Arestaurant_host%2Fhostess%7Cl%3A1560%3Amililani%7Cc%3A104%3Acalifornia_pizza_kitchen&amp;utm_content=day-wednesday" rel="nofollow">Restaurant Host/Hostess</a>
</li>

<li><a href="https://higherme.com/jobs/58651470bc4ce?utm_source=craigslist&amp;utm_medium=job_board&amp;utm_campaign=j%3A4278%3Arestaurant_dishwasher%7Cl%3A1560%3Amililani%7Cc%3A104%3Acalifornia_pizza_kitchen&amp;utm_content=day-wednesday" rel="nofollow">Restaurant Dishwasher</a></li>

<li><a href="https://higherme.com/jobs/586514728b90f?utm_source=craigslist&amp;utm_medium=job_board&amp;utm_campaign=j%3A4279%3Arestaurant_servers%7Cl%3A1560%3Amililani%7Cc%3A104%3Acalifornia_pizza_kitchen&amp;utm_content=day-wednesday" rel="nofollow">Restaurant Servers</a></li>

<li><a href="https://higherme.com/jobs/5865147407ad0?utm_source=craigslist&amp;utm_medium=job_board&amp;utm_campaign=j%3A4280%3Arestaurant_take-out_server%7Cl%3A1560%3Amililani%7Cc%3A104%3Acalifornia_pizza_kitchen&amp;utm_content=day-wednesday" rel="nofollow">Restaurant Take-out Server</a>
</li></ul></strong>

<br>
We are looking for passionate individuals with hospitality in their soul. We have a full training program that won't leave you hanging, long time employees who love their job and meeting new people, free food for performance, daily meal discounts, gift cards, weekly contests, cash prizes, etc. What more could you ask for in the #bestjobeverCPK? 
<br><br>

